{"id":"428835640537739_507840855970550","type":"status","created_time":"2013-07-18T16:46:30+0000","message":"Chhatrashibir\u2019s processions, picketing and road blockade on 4th day hartal:\n\nLeaders of Bangladesh Islami Chhatrashibir said, \u201cThe government still continues with its conspiracies to kill Jamaat leaders by a tribunal dubbed \u2018partisan\u2019 and \u2018controversial\u2019 by principal international organizations like International Bar Council, Human Rights Watch and other international media. They made a blueprint to uproot Islamic Movement from this land by the tribunal set up by some black jungle laws. As a part of this blueprint, this tribunal has been going on with its ill mission by handing down some farcical verdicts against innocent top Jamaat leaders.\u201d\n\nLeaders said, \u201cThe controversial farcical rulings of the tribunal duly channeled people\u2019s tolerance beyond the bound and the people came outside in protest against the verdicts of the partizan tribunal. The people passed their \u2018no confidence\u2019 motion to this tribunal by effectualizing continuous shutdowns at the cost of many lives even in this month of Ramadan.\u201d\n\nThey said so while addressing the gatherings held after processions are launched, picketing is done and roads are blocked during the shutdown called in protest against the unjust and farcical death penalty verdict of the Awami tribunal unto Jamaat-e-Islami Secretary-General and the former Bangladesh Minister Ali Ahsan Muhammad Mujahid. Various units of Bangladesh Islami Chhatrashibir brought out processions, did picketing, blocked road and highways and held gatherings in support of today\u2019s shutdown called by Jamaat."}